        <Summary>Command line oriented, sqlite powered, todo list system</Summary>
        <Description>yokadi helps you organize all the things you have to do and you must not forget. It aims to be simple, intuitive and very efficient. In Yokadi you manage projects, which contains tasks. At the minimum, a task has a title, but it can also have a description, a due date, an urgency or keywords.</Description>
